{"tid":1078140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛州槍擊案再有倖存者自盡","createTime":"2019-03-26T05:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T07:44:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb212adfa5d933f07d9024804497b07b63ba014e","tid":1078140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190326/20641581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F20641581&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=fef31044\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F20641581&h=efca3500\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190326/20641581</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佛州槍擊案再有倖存者自盡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190326/large/26wh110p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190326%2Flarge%2F26wh110p.jpg&h=5e6fff91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喪失了兩名摯友的倖存者艾洛選擇了結生命。<br />\n<br />\n美國佛羅里達州帕克蘭去年發生釀成17人死亡的高中槍擊案，繼本月17日有位深受創傷後遺症困擾的19歲倖存者用手槍自盡後，警方證實該所高中再有學生「明顯地」因自殺身亡，引起外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n患創傷後遺症<br />\n<br />\n佛州的科勒爾斯普林斯警方指，該名學生在上周六傍晚死去，由於尚未收到其驗屍報告，暫時把死因稱作「明顯地」因自殺死亡。<br />\n<br />\n佛州《邁阿密先驅報》報道，去年的槍擊案發生時，死者正是事發的「瑪喬麗斯通曼道格拉斯高中」的高二男學生；但其自殺與槍擊案的關係未明。<br />\n<br />\n一周前，在槍擊案喪失了兩名摯友的倖存者艾洛（Sydney Aiello）也選擇了結生命。她的母親指，槍擊案發生後，艾洛一直受着「倖存者罪惡感」所困，為仍然活着深感自責，又確診患上創傷後遺症。艾洛的家人上周五為她辦葬禮。<br />\n<br />\n接連兩宗的自殺案再喚起當地人對學生精神健康支援的關注。在槍擊案生還後積極倡議槍械管制的霍格（David Hogg）指，學校要在精神健康方面，投放更多資源，「到底我們要因自殺失去多少同伴，才可讓政府或學校採取任何行動？」<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美國有線新聞網絡  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n新西蘭總理徹查槍擊案起因"},{"pid":"7d6881bc64ecad3fecbffe11c66cf5a0c79a7ae4","tid":1078140,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"死神來了"},{"pid":"ecd4b467eb6b0d4cfc21bdeeeb6e3c89cb1d0d4d","tid":1078140,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}